PROCEDURE main()

	local oClass
	local cResponse := "Error"
	local hParams 	 := AP_GetPairs()

	switch hParams['cmd']
		case 'articulos' 	; oClass := TArticulos():New() 	; EXIT
		case 'clientes' 	; oClass := TClientes():New() 	; EXIT
	end

	if oClass != NIL
		switch AP_Method()
			case 'GET' 		; oClass:Select() 	; EXIT
			case 'POST' 	; oClass:Edit(.T.) 	; EXIT
			case 'PUT' 		; oClass:Edit(.F.)	; EXIT
			case 'DELETE'  ; oClass:Delete() 	; EXIT
		end
		cResponse := oClass:Response()
	endif

	? cResponse
return

PROCEDURE main()

	local oClass
	local cResponse := "Error"
	local hParams 	 := AP_GetPairs()

	switch hParams['cmd']
		case 'articulos' 	; oClass := TArticulos():New() 	; EXIT
		case 'clientes' 	; oClass := TClientes():New() 	; EXIT
	end

	if oClass != NIL
		switch AP_Method()
			case 'GET' 		; oClass:Select() 	; EXIT
			case 'POST' 	; oClass:Edit(.T.) 	; EXIT
			case 'PUT' 		; oClass:Edit(.F.)	; EXIT
			case 'DELETE'  ; oClass:Delete() 	; EXIT
		end
		cResponse := oClass:Response()
	endif

	? cResponse
return

//--------------------------------------------------------------------------//
// Modulos (despues de main)
//--------------------------------------------------------------------------//
